                                        'text' => 'At 14th level, choose two additional spells from any class, including this one. A spell you choose must be of a level you can cast, as shown on the Bard table, or a cantrip.
  The chosen spells count as bard spells for you and are included in the number in the Spells Known column of the Bard table.',
