                                'content' => array(
                                    0 => array(
                                        'name' => 'Stroke of Luck',
                                        'text' => 'At 20th level, you have an uncanny knack for succeeding when you need to. If your attack misses a target within range, you can turn the miss into a hit. Alternatively, if you fail an ability check, you can treat the d20 roll as a 20.
  Once you use this feature, you can\'t use it again until you finish a short or long rest.',
                                    ),
                                ),
