                                    14 => array(
                                        'name' => 'Chosen of the Gods: Tempest',
                                        'text' => 'Add the following spells to your list of known spells when you reach the indicated level. These spells count as sorcerer spells for you and do not count against your number of spells known. You may also find these spells in the Cleric (Tempest) spell list.

