                                'content' => array(
                                    0 => array(
                                        'name' => 'Sanguine Mastery',
                                        'text' => 'Upon becoming 20th level, your crimson rite is perfected, no longer requiring visceral sacrifice. When you have an active crimson rite, you no longer reduce your maximum hit points and you take no damage when amplifying blood curses. In addition, when you are below one fourth of your current maximum hit points and conscious, all your crimson rite damage dice are maximized.',
