                                        'name' => 'Primal Path: Path of the Totem Warrior',
                                        'text' => 'The Path of the Totem Warrior is a spiritual journey, as the barbarian accepts a spirit animal as guide, protector, and inspiration. In battle, your totem spirit fills you with supernatural might, adding magical fuel to your barbarian rage.

